'''Eduardo Rafael Cáceres Lehnhoff''' served as [[Vice President of Guatemala]] from 1 July 1970 to 1 July 1974 in the cabinet of [[Carlos Manuel Arana Osorio|Carlos Arana]].

Died 31 January 1980 in the [[Burning of the Spanish Embassy]] in Guatemala-City.<ref>"[http://www.aquiguatemala.net/presidentes/manuel_a_osorio.html Carlos Manuel Arana Osorio profile]"</ref>

